<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> On becoming aware of them, insurance undertakings shall inform the competent authorities of their home Member States of any acquisitions or disposals of holdings in their capital that cause holdings to exceed or fall below any of the tresholds referred to in paragraphs 1 and 2. </inglise>
