<inglise> In addition, notwithstanding paragraphs 1 and 4, the Member States may, under provisions laid down by law, authorize the disclosure of certain information to other departments of their central government administrations responsible for legislation on the supervision of credit institutions, financial institutions, investment services and insurance companies and to inspectors acting on behalf of those departments. </inglise>
<eesti> L&otilde;igetest 1 ja 4 olenemata v&otilde;ivad liikmesriigid vastavalt seaduses s&auml;testatud eeskirjadele lubada teatud andmete edastamist ka teistele keskvalitsuse asutustele, kes vastutavad krediidiasutuste, finantseerimisasutuste, investeerimisteenuste ja kindlustusseltside j&auml;relevalve alaste &otilde;igusaktide eest, ning nende asutuste nimel tegutsevatele inspektoritele. </eesti>
