<eesti> Artikkel 20 </eesti>
<inglise> The assets covering the technical provisions shall take account of the type of business carried on by an undertaking in such a way as to secure the safety, yield and marketability of its investments, which the undertaking shall ensure are diversified and adequately spread. </inglise>
