<inglise> The home Member State shall lay down more detailed rules fixing the conditions for the use of acceptable assets; in this connection, it may require valuable security or guarantees, particularly in the case of debts owed by reinsurers. </inglise>
<eesti> P&auml;ritoluliikmesriik s&auml;testab &uuml;ksikasjalikumad eeskirjad, mis kinnitavad lubatavate varade kasutamise tingimused; seoses sellega v&otilde;ib ta n&otilde;uda v&auml;&auml;rtuslikke tagatisi v&otilde;i garantiisid, eriti edasikindlustajate v&otilde;lgade korral. </eesti>
<inglise> In the determination and the application of the rules which it lays down, the home Member State shall, in particular, ensure that the following principles are complied with: </inglise>
<eesti> S&auml;testatavate eeskirjade m&auml;&auml;ratlemise ja kohaldamisega tagab liikmesriik eesk&auml;tt j&auml;rgmiste p&otilde;him&otilde;tete j&auml;rgimise: </eesti>
<inglise> (i) assets covering technical provisions shall be valued net of any debts arising out of their acquisition; </inglise>
<eesti> i) kindlustustehnilisi eraldisi tagavate varade hindamisel arvatakse maha nende omandamisel tekkinud v&otilde;lad; </eesti>
<inglise> (ii) all assets must be valued on a prudent basis, allowing for the risk of any amounts' not being realizable. </inglise>
<eesti> ii) k&otilde;ik varad tuleb hinnata usaldusv&auml;&auml;rsel alusel, arvestades riski, et summad ei ole realiseeritavad. </eesti>
<inglise> In particular, tangible fixed assets other than land and buildings may be accepted as cover for technical provisions only if they are valued on the basis of prudent amortization; </inglise>
<eesti> Eriti v&otilde;ib materiaalset p&otilde;hivara peale maa ja ehitiste kindlustustehniliste eraldiste tagamiseks heaks kiita ainult juhul, kui seda hinnatakse usaldusv&auml;&auml;rse amortisatsiooni alusel; </eesti>
<inglise> (iii) loans, whether to undertakings, to State authorities or international organizations, to local or regional authorities or to natural persons, may be accepted as cover for technical provisions only if there are sufficient guarantees as to their security, whether these are based on the status of the borrower, mortgages, bank guarantees or guarantees granted by insurance undertakings or other forms of security; </inglise>
<eesti> iii) laene kindlustusseltsidele, riigiasutustele v&otilde;i rahvusvahelistele organisatsioonidele, kohalikele v&otilde;i piirkondlikele asutustele v&otilde;i f&uuml;&uuml;silistele isikutele v&otilde;ib heaks kiita kindlustustehniliste eraldiste kattena ainult juhul, kui nende tagatise kohta on piisavad garantiid, mis p&otilde;hinevad kas laenusaaja seisundil, h&uuml;poteekidel, pangagarantiidel v&otilde;i kindlustusseltside antud garantiidel v&otilde;i muudel tagatisevormidel; </eesti>
<inglise> (iv) derivative instruments such as options, futures and swaps in connection with assets covering technical provisions may be used in so far as they contribute to a reduction of investment risks or facilitate efficient portfolio management. </inglise>
