<inglise> - alteration of the minimum guarantee fund provided for in Article 17 (2) of Directive 73/239/EEC to take account of economic and financial developments, </inglise>
<eesti> - direktiivi 73/239/EM&Uuml; artikli 17 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud minimaalse garantiifondi muutmine, et v&otilde;tta arvesse majanduslikku ja finantsarengut, </eesti>
<inglise> - amendments, to take account of the creation of new financial instruments, to the list of assets acceptable as cover for technical provisions set out in Article 21 of this Directive and to the rules on the spreading of investments laid down in Article 22, </inglise>
